Package Model

Class Blockade

java.lang.Object
Model.Blockade
All Implemented Interfaces:
Order
public class Blockade extends Object implements Order
Class containing logic for implementation of Blockade order Blockade cards change one of your territories to a neutral and multiply the number of armies on that territory by 3 times. They're useful for creating a defensive blockade, among other uses.
Author:
Alekhya K
